name: Prototype Amber
desc: A dully gilded catalyst secretly guarded in the Blackcliff Forge. It seems to glow with the very light from the sky.
skill_desc: Using an Elemental Burst regenerates 4/4.5/5/5.5/6Energy every 2s for 6s. All party members will regenerate 4%/4.5%/5%/5.5%/6% HP every 2s for this duration.
